name: Till Death Do Us Apart
description: A few years ago I started exploring photograms-rayograph, an alternative process technique that used mechanical and chemical process, in a dark room. I started by making a photogram of 2 dead birds that I found in a trash can at one of the bird and animal markets in Yogyakarta. Since then, I have also started my photography project, on the issue of chirping bird exploitation. This image 1500 px X 1500 px, 72 dpi
